message.body: Nah, that looks like a Volvo. The tail light is too tall.
Whoooo! Thank you, I feel better. Of course, I also feel bad about the person in the car.
Yes. Definitely. How are feeling this week?
The f-ing city decided to tow my car and didn't tell me!
I was on the phone for a while with the special department telling them how upset I am!
I had a feeling they may have towed it... I thought you called around. Why did they tow it?

I did, more than once. They admitted that it was the 12th district's fault for not letting me know. I was pissed it was almost a week before I found out. It was for inspection. They had to go to the captain about it.
I'm glad you got it back!.... Or will get it back? Feeling better?
